longBusinessSummary: ioneer Ltd explores for and develops mineral properties in North America. It focuses on developing the 100% owned Rhyolite Ridge lithium-boron project located in Nevada, the United States. The company was formerly known as Global Geoscience Limited and changed its name to ioneer Ltd in November 2018. ioneer Ltd was incorporated in 2001 and is based in North Sydney, Australia.
